.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Frental-market-moderates-ncr-sees-strong-demand-report%2Farticleshow%2F125527716.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20husband%20died%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20launching%20a%20business.%20I%20pivoted%20my%20career%20at%2055%20to%20take%20over%2C%20and%20it's%20helped%20with%20my%20grief.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221479%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jacqueline%20Gathers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69123cf746c4547ecb057f1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221109%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jacqueline%20Gathers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJacqueline%20Gathers%20is%20a%20home%20inspector%20and%20owner%20of%20a%20Pillar%20to%20Post%20franchise%20in%20Brooklyn.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20worked%20for%20New%20York%20City%20for%2030%20years%20and%20had%20no%20interest%20in%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20her%20husband%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2055%2C%20Jacqueline%20became%20a%20home%20inspector.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fjacqueline-gathers-ptp%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJacqueline%20Gathers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20owner%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjacquelinegathers.pillartopost.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJS%20Gathers%20Pillar%20to%20Post%20Home%20Inspectors%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20franchise.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20third-generation%20civil%20servant.%20I%20spent%2030%20years%20at%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Housing%20Authority.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychological-tricks-enjoy-your-job-career-strategy-2016-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenjoyed%20the%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20felt%20that%20I%20was%20helping%20people%20find%20safe%20and%20affordable%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20joined%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fsection-8-homeownership-program%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHousing%20Authority%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20in%20the%20'80s%2C%20my%20dad%20insisted%20I%20sign%20up%20for%20early%20retirement.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20extra%20contributions%20to%20my%20pension%20seemed%20expensive%2C%20but%20my%20dad%20assured%20me%20the%20investment%20was%20worthwhile.%20A%20lot%20could%20change%20between%2055%20and%2062%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20being%20able%20to%20retire%20early%20would%20give%20me%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20so%20right.%20Decades%20later%2C%20that%20decision%20allowed%20me%20to%20take%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-advice-from-my-dad-who-retired-early-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearly%20retirement%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20order%20to%20be%20home%20with%20my%20husband%2C%20Joseph%2C%20as%20he%20fought%20brain%20cancer.%20Joseph%20died%20when%20he%20was%2058%2C%20and%20I%20was%2055.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ba08bcb-e61e-4495-b751-4dae96c37bc7%5C%22%3EWhen%20my%20husband%20died%2C%20I%20considered%20selling%20our%20franchise%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little%20more%20than%20a%20year%20before%20he%20died%2C%20Joseph%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20take%20me%20into%20the%20city.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstopping-date-night-saved-my-marriage-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edate%20night%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20when%20I%20came%20out%20in%20my%20heels%2C%20he%20told%20me%20to%20put%20on%20something%20more%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurns%20out%2C%20he%20wasn't%20taking%20me%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-dinners-that-are-impressive-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efancy%20dinner%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20we%20were%20going%20to%20the%20franchise%20expo.%20That's%20when%20Joseph%20dropped%20the%20bomb%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20purchase%20a%20franchise.%20I%20said%20OK%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20particularly%20interested.%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20plans%20to%20be%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoseph%20researched%20Pillar%20to%20Post%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-inspectors-tips-before-buying-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehome%20inspection%3C%2Fa%3E%20company%2C%20and%20underwent%20training%20with%20the%20organization.%20But%20before%20he%20could%20open%20the%20franchise%2C%20he%20died.%20The%20company%20offered%20to%20repurchase%20our%20franchise.%20I%20was%20tempted%2C%20but%20then%20I%20thought%20about%20how%20hard%20Joseph%20had%20worked%20to%20prepare%20the%20business.%20I%20decided%20to%20launch%20it%20in%20his%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22542921f2-b8a8-4659-9fba-9e7d9f46f7af%5C%22%3EIt%20took%20time%20to%20build%20a%20business%20as%20a%20Black%20female%20inspector%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20things%20got%20scary.%20I%20had%20retired%20from%20the%20Housing%20Authority%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20nothing%20about%20home%20inspections.%20I%20had%20to%20train%20with%20Pillar%20and%20Post%20and%20obtain%20a%20license%20from%20the%20state%20of%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20home%20inspectors%20don't%20look%20like%20me.%20That%20became%20abundantly%20clear%20when%20I%20tried%20to%20work%20in%20Staten%20Island%20and%20other%20areas%20known%20for%20their%20racial%20tension.%20I%20wasn't%20well%20received%20there.%20However%2C%20when%20I%20expanded%20into%20more%20diverse%20areas%20of%20the%20city%2C%20such%20as%20Flatbush%2C%20Brownsville%2C%20and%20East%20New%20York%2C%20business%20picked%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20initially%20got%20to%20work%20when%20other%20inspectors%20didn't%20show%20up.%20In%20those%20situations%2C%20my%20customer%20service%20skills%20from%20the%20Housing%20Authority%20helped%20me%20stand%20out%20from%20the%20crowd.%20Plus%2C%20people%20saw%20I%20knew%20what%20I%20was%20talking%20about.%20Before%20long%2C%20people%20were%20asking%20for%20%26quot%3Bthat%20Black%20lady%20inspector%20in%20Brooklyn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f110bf0b-d603-4417-affe-7e5073a49ca4%5C%22%3EI%20found%20my%20niche%20with%20first-time%20buyers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20year%2C%20I%20would%20go%20to%20work%2C%20then%20come%20home%20and%20cry.%20The%20business%20was%20a%20huge%20distraction%20and%20gave%20me%20a%20reason%20to%20get%20up%20every%20day%2C%20but%20my%20grief%20was%20raw%2C%20and%20the%20tears%20were%20never%20far.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20started%20crying%20less%20and%20focusing%20more%20on%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it's%20been%20eight%20years%20since%20Joseph%20died%2C%20and%20seven%20years%20since%20I%20launched%20the%20business.%20I've%20created%20a%20niche%20working%20with%20first-time%20homebuyers.%20I%20also%20work%20with%20educational%20nonprofits%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParticularly%20in%20my%20community%2C%20first-time%20buyers%20may%20be%20the%20first%20people%20in%20their%20family%20to%20ever%20own%20a%20property.%20They%20need%20guidance%20and%20a%20relationship%20that%20doesn't%20end%20once%20the%20sale%20closes.%20My%20clients%20can%20reach%20back%20out%20to%20me%20whenever%20they%20have%20questions%20about%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c52b8d87-871c-4e19-81d1-5bf03a8450b8%5C%22%3EI've%20set%20an%20example%20for%20my%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJoseph%20and%20I%20always%20lived%20below%20our%20means%20and%20planned%20to%20travel%20in%20retirement.%20In%20addition%20to%20running%20the%20business%20%E2%80%94%20which%20still%20bears%20his%20name%20%E2%80%94%20I%20try%20to%20take%20two%20international%20trips%20in%20his%20honor%20each%20year.%20Our%20first%20grandchild%20was%20recently%20born%20in%20Guam%2C%20and%20I'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20spending%20time%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20surprised%20to%20find%20myself%20an%20entrepreneur%20at%2064.%20I%20never%20imagined%20myself%20running%20a%20business%2C%20let%20alone%20one%20that's%20super%20successful.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20I've%20set%20an%20example%20for%20my%20three%20kids%3A%20sometimes%20in%20life%2C%20you%20get%20curveballs%2C%20and%20you%20just%20have%20to%20keep%20pushing.%20There's%20something%20else%20waiting%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarted-home-inspection-business-fifties-after-my-husband-died-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763937481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69123cf746c4547ecb057f1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarted-home-inspection-business-fifties-after-my-husband-died-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20her%20husband%20died%20before%20launching%20their%20franchise%2C%20Jacqueline%20Gathers%20kept%20his%20dream%20alive%20%E2%80%94%20and%20became%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%20at%2064.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarted-home-inspection-business-fifties-after-my-husband-died-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nina%20Lin%20sparks%20backlash%20after%20cursing%20near%20a%2013%20year%20old%20as%20RayAsianBoy%20Twitch%20stream%20collab%20creates%20new%20debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763937060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-125526650%2Cimgsize-737379.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fnina-lin-sparks-backlash-after-cursing-near-a-13-year-old-as