0California%2C%20she%20continued%20to%20run%20the%20business%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20one%20who%20spoke%20English.%20So%20I%20took%20all%20the%20customer%20phone%20calls%2C%20I%20dealt%20with%20the%20billing%2C%20the%20inspections%2C%20all%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%2C%20she%20said%2C%20taught%20her%20the%20value%20of%20resilience%20%E2%80%94%20a%20principle%20that%20continues%20to%20guide%20her%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20scientist%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20resilient%20because%20science%20is%20a%20non-linear%20journey.%20Nobody%20has%20all%20the%20solutions.%20You%20have%20to%20go%20through%20such%20a%20challenge%20to%20find%20an%20answer.%20And%20as%20an%20immigrant%2C%20you%20learn%20to%20be%20resilient%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20World%20Labs%2C%20Li%20has%20big%20ambitions.%20She%20is%20working%20on%20building%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-yann-lecun-llm-world-model-intelligence-criticism-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworld%20models%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20are%20AI%20models%20that%20leverage%20spatial%20intelligence%2C%20which%20Li%20says%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ability%20for%20AI%20to%20understand%2C%20perceive%2C%20reason%20and%20interact%20%5Bwith%20the%20world%5D.%20It%20comes%20from%20a%20continuation%20of%20visual%20intelligence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20number%20of%20AI%20experts%20believe%20that%20world%20models%20are%20what%20will%20propel%20the%20AI%20revolution%20into%20its%20next%20phase.%20Some%20believe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flimits-large-language-models-chatgpt-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-openai-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elarge-language%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20trained%20on%2C%20as%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20language%2C%20and%20which%20the%20leading%20products%20are%20now%20based%2C%20are%20limited