Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feden-green-hiring-indoor-farming-workers-agriculture-jobs-benefits-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplant%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20drop%20their%20children%20off%2C%20we'll%20have%20some%20that%20are%20still%20half%20asleep%20on%20their%20parents'%20shoulders.%20However%2C%20they%20typically%20run%20excited%20to%20see%20their%20friends.%20We'll%20have%20activities%20that%20are%20already%20planned%20out%20on%20the%20table%20to%20engage%20them%20as%20they%20transition%20into%20the%20classroom.%20Once%20they're%20settled%20in%2C%20then%20they%20have%20some%20free%20play%20and%20can%20explore%20our%20different%20learning%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20these%20plants%20were%20established%20in%201996%20and%201986%2C%20respectively%2C%20there%20were%20few%20quality%20childcare%20centers%20available%2C%20so%20Toyota%20recognized%20the%20need%20to%20provide%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-100-brands-according-to-millennials-from-netflix-to-walmart-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eservice%20for%20its%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20our%20nighttime%20day%20care%20service%20is%20in%20such%20high%20demand.%20At%20our%20Princeton%20childcare%20center%2C%20164%20children%20are%20enrolled%20during%20the%20day%2C%20while%2044%20are%20enrolled%20at%20night.%20In%20Georgetown%2C%20about%20159%20kids%20are%20enrolled%20in%20the%20day%20program%2C%20and%2032%20are%20enrolled%20at%20night.%20The%20center%20is%20also%20open%20on%20Saturdays.%20Around%2025%20are%20booked%20in%20the%20day%20and%20around%2020%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221028%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Toddler%20playing%20with%20rock%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6914cd22e1a9cbb014de1140%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22771%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKids%20during%20the%20night%20program%20stay%20up%20and%20do%20the%20same%20things%20as%20kids%20during%20the%20day%20program.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Bright%20Horizons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKeeping%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-your-bedtime-routine-is-bad-for-you-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enighttime%20routine%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20close%20as%20possible%20to%20our%20daytime%20routine%20is%20a%20strong%20principle%20that%20we%20have%20implemented%20throughout%20the%20years.%20It's%20that%20equity%20piece.%20We%20don't%20want%20our%20children%20or%20our%20families%20to%20feel%20that%20they%20are%20missing%20out%20because%20of%20the%20shift%20that%20they%20are%20on.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20it's%20Grandparents%20Day%20during%20the%20day%2C%20we%20will%20replicate%20that%20at%20night.%20We%20often%20say%20that%20the%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20we%20swap%20sunscreen%20for%20bug%20spray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eeba782a-6815-49f5-bac2-450ab21ec301%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20so%20fun%20to%20be%20outside%20with%20the%20kids%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20night%20runs%20like%20this%3A%20once%20they%20have%20settled%20in%2C%20they%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhealthy-breakfast-ideas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeat%20breakfast%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Then%20they%20will%20play%20outside%2C%20and%20come%20back%20in%20for%20some%20activities%20and%20projects.%20We%20follow%20a%20curriculum%2C%20but%20we%20also%20discuss%20with%20the%20children%20what%20they%20are%20interested%20in%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20typically%20have%20lunch%20around%2010%3A30%20p.m.%20Then%2C%20after%20lunch%2C%20just%20like%20daytime%20children%2C%20some%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-long-should-i-nap%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etake%20a%20nap%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20up%20to%20two%20hours%20at%20this%20point.%20For%20those%20children%20who%20don't%20nap%2C%20they'll%20transition%20into%20rest%20time%20and%20quiet%20activities.%20We%20offer%20%26quot%3Binner%20explorer%2C%26quot%3B%20our%20mindfulness%20program%20that%20helps%20calm%20the%20mind%20and%20body%2C%20promoting%20relaxation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%2C%20it%20will%20be%20snack%20time%2C%20and%20we%20will%20go%20outside%20again.%20They%20return%20for%20some%20additional%20curriculum%20time%2C%20and%20then%2C%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20shift%2C%20they'll%20have%20some%20extra%20learning%20time.%20It%20will%20then%20be%20time%20to%20go%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20actually%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20being%20outside%20with%20the%20children%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-if-you-wake-up-in-the-night-and-cant-fall-back-asleep-2017-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20middle%20of%20the%20night%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20are%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20cornfield%2C%20so%20we%20have%20high%20fencing%20and%20stadium%20lighting.%20There%20is%20nature%20outside%20to%20contend%20with%2C%20but%20we%20know%20how%20to%20keep%20safe.%20The%20children%20like%20to%20holler%20at%20the%20deer%2C%20and%20we%20often%20get%20mice%20wandering%20in.%20We%20might%20also%20see%20the%20occasional%20coyote%2C%20and%20the%20children%20love%20it.%20The%20lights%20are%20so%20bright%20you%20often%20forget%20what%20time%20of%20night%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e433b7ae-60ba-4256-a22b-6a51601c04ab%5C%22%3EKids%20can%20come%20starting%20at%207%20weeks%20up%20to%20before%20they%20start%20kindergarten%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20children%20start%20with%20us%20at%20around%207%20weeks%20old%20and%20stay%20with%20us%20until%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-twins-started-kindergarten-a-year-late-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebegin%20kindergarten%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Typically%2C%20night%20shift%20families%20have%20it%20made%20in%20this%20regard%20-%20their%20babies%20sleep%20the%20best%20and%20they%20don't%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20often%20asked%20if%20we%20plan%20to%20open%20a%20kindergarten%20program%2C%20but%20there%20are%20no%20plans%20at%20the%20moment.%20We%20do%20everything%20we%20can%20to%20support%20them%20in%20their%20transition%20into%20kindergarten%20and%20school%2C%20where%20they%20will%20have%20to%20adhere%20to%20more%20conventional%20hours.%20We'll%20lengthen%20naptime%2C%20so%20by%20the%20time%20they're%20graduating%2C%20they'll%20be%20sleeping%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221348%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20at%20Bright%20Horizons%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6914cefae1a9cbb014de117c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221011%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBright%20Horizons%20works%20with%20families%20whose%20kids%20are%20soon%20moving%20into%20regular%20school%20hours.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Bright%20Horizons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20families%20will%20also%20tend%20to%20take%20off%20the%20week%20before%20school%20starts%2C%20to%20get%20into%20that%20new%20groove%20and%20routine.%20Parents%20aren't%20guaranteed%20to%20be%20moved%20to%20the%20day%20shift%20when%20their%20children%20start%20kindergarten%2C%20so%20they%20may%20have%20to%20drop%20their%20children%20off%20at%20Grandma's%20and%20Grandpa's%20or%20arrange%20for%20someone%20to%20come%20to%20their%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Kentucky%2C%20though%2C%20we%20do%20have%20a%20school-age%20program.%20The%20children%20have%20their%20own%20beds%2C%20dressers%2C%20locker%20rooms%2C%20and%20showers%2C%20and%20they%20will%20go%20to%20bed%20by%209%3A30%20p.m.%20while%20their%20parents%20work%20the%20night%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da80c018-eb1a-4572-aa81-25877691181e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20facilities%20are%20crucial%20to%20working%20parents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20tend%20to%20have%20issues%20with%20our%20children%20not%20being%20rested%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20they%20have%20learned%20to%20follow%20their%20parents'%20schedules%2C%20and%20they%20start%20young%20enough%20that%20it's%20easy%20for%20them%20to%20adapt.%20Sometimes%2C%20life%20admin%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20care%20of%20during%20the%20day%2C%20and%20we%20might%20not%20get%20a%20full%20night's%20sleep%2C%20but%20that%20happens%20to%20all%20of%20us%20at%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20a%20doctor's%20office%2C%20pharmacy%2C%20and%20store%20on-site%2C%20and%20we%20also%20have%20health%20professionals%20visit%20us%20to%20support%20the%20children.%20For%20example%2C%20twice%20a%20year%20a%20local%20hospital%20will%20send%20in%20occupational%2C%20speech%2C%20developmental%2C%20social%20and%20emotional%20therapists%2C%20and%20they%20will%20come%20in%20and%20do%20developmental%20screenings.%20They%20will%20bill%20the%20health%20insurance%20providers%20directly%20at%20no%20cost%20to%20the%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20have%20optometrists%20and%20dentists%20come%20on-site.%20Then%20we%20have%20professional%20family%20photographers%20come%20too.%20These%20events%20occur%20both%20during%20the%20day%20and%20night%2C%20benefiting%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20am%20a%20regional%20manager%20now%2C%20I%20still%20will%20go%20in%20and%20work%20nights.%20I%20just%20drink%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiet-coke-gave-up-for-month-effects-on-body-soda-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eextra%20Diet%20Coke%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20also%20have%20an%20almost%2019-year-old%20autistic%20son%20who%20has%20never%20slept%20well%20anyway%2C%20so%20he's%20been%20conditioning%20me%20my%20entire%20adult%20life%20to%20do%20this%20kind%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20big%20misconception%20that%20we%20just%20keep%20the%20kids%20up%20all%20night.%20Yes%2C%20we%20do%20that.%20But%20that%20work-life%20balance%20is%20critical%20for%20parents%20who%20work%20hard.%20That's%20why%20we%20pioneered%20this%20style%20of%20childcare%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20works%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fovernight-daycare-manager-shares-how-it-works-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763925421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6914d5c4e1a9cbb014de120b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fovernight-daycare-manager-shares-how-it-works-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amanda%20Yochum%20manages%20overnight%20childcare%20centers%20where%20kids%20play%2C%20learn%2C%20and%20thrive%20while%20their%20parents%20work%20night%20shifts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(MaryLou%20Costa)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A72%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fovernight-daycare-manager-shares-how-it-works-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranveer%20reveals%20Udaipur%20was%20'lucky'%20for%20romance%20with%20Deepika%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763924921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-125524358%2Cimgsize-33052.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-singh-reveals-romance-with-deepika-padukone-began-on-ram-leela-sets-says-udaipur-is-lucky-for-love-stories-as-he-gives-dua-a-shoutout-watch%2Farticleshow%2F125524407.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F125524407.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERanveer%20Singh%20charmed%20guests%20at%20a%20sangeet%20by%20sharing%20how%20Udaipur%20sparked%20his%20romance%20with%20Deepika%20Padukone%20during%20'Ram-Leela'.%20He%