iv%3EPressure-cooked%20rice%20is%20hands-off.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pressure%20cooker%20on%20a%20counter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c8aad8b1834fe31166427a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESteven%20John%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20I%20measured%20out%20a%20cup%20of%20rice%2C%20which%20I%20then%20rinsed%20well%20under%20tepid%20water.%20Next%2C%20I%20added%20%C2%BD%20cup%20of%20broth%2C%20%C2%BD%20cup%20of%20water%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20olive%20oil%20to%20a%20lightly%20sprayed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fhow-to-use-an-instant-pot%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInstant%20Pot%20pressure%20cooker%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20secured%20the%20lid%20and%20pressed%20the%20%26quot%3Brice%26quot%3B%20button.%20And%20that's%20it%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20beauty%20of%20this%20device.%20It's%20so%20easy%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20brief%20period%20of%20pressurization%2C%20the%20rice%20cooked%20for%20all%20of%2012%20minutes%2C%20then%20the%20appliance%20beeped%2C%20indicating%20it%20was%20rice%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20still%20feels%20like%20a%20reliable%20way%20to%20quickly%20cook%20the%20grain.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223668%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rice%20in%20a%20pressure%20cooker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c8ab0fb1834fe311664288%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222751%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESteven%20John%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20pressure-cooked%20rice%20was%20plenty%20flavorful%20and%20had%20a%20soft%2C%20though%20not%20quite%20fluffy%20texture.%20All%20of%20the%20grains%20of%20rice%20were%20cooked%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20was%20so%20easy%2C%20and%20I%20have%20no%20big%20complaints%20about%20the%20taste%20