%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-cook-rice%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecooking%20rice%20in%20a%20microwave%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20cross-referenced%20at%20least%20a%20half-dozen%20recipes%20I%20found%20online%2C%20so%20I'm%20confident%20my%20approach%20was%20decent.%20But%20the%20outcome%3F%20I%20can%20hardly%20describe%20it%20as%20such.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rinsed%20the%20rice%2C%20combined%20it%20with%201%20%C2%BE%20cups%20of%20my%20water-broth%20blend%2C%20and%20added%20the%20olive%20oil%20to%20a%20microwave-safe%20glass%20container.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20I%20partially%20secured%20the%20container's%20lid%20%E2%80%94%20not%20too%20tightly%2C%20as%20I%20didn't%20want%20it%20to%20explode%20%E2%80%94%20and%20popped%20the%20rice%20in%20the%20microwave%20on%20full%20power%20for%20five%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20microwaved%20it%20for%20another%2015%20minutes%20on%20half%20power%20and%20let%20it%20rest%20for%20an%20additional%20five%20minutes%20before%20retrieving%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20won't%20be%20using%20this%20appliance%20for%20rice%20again.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bowls%20of%20white%20rice%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c8ac34b8b41a9673f9c82e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22916%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESteven%20John%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20low%20expectations%2C%20but%20I%20was%20still%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20microwaved%20rice%20was%20clumpy%20and%20dried%20out%2C%20except%20for%20the%20largest%20gobs%2C%20which%20were%20gummy%20and%20unevenly%20cooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20a%20generous%20dose%20of%20a%20sauce%20and%20further%20cooking%20in%20a%20frying%20pan%20could%20have%20made%20this%20rice%20tasty.%20I%20took%20three%20or%20four%20bites%20and%20then%20composted%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe