20within%20Search%20%E2%80%94%20Google's%20most%20prized%20business%20%E2%80%94%20on%20day%20one%2C%20a%20strong%20signal%20that%20after%20three%20years%20the%20company%20had%20gotten%20its%20ducks%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20big%20questions%20that%20Google%20is%20still%20grappling%20with%20as%20it%20rebuilds%20its%20image%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%20OpenAI's%20first-mover%20advantage%20meant%20that%20ChatGPT%20has%20become%20the%20%26quot%3BKleenex%26quot%3B%20of%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20the%20name%20that%20everyone%20associates%20with%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20will%20be%20tough%20for%20Google%20to%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20a%20series%20exploring%20the%20changing%20online%20search%20landscape%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20consumers%2C%20media%20companies%2C%20advertisers%2C%20and%20tech%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedia-startups-post-google-zero-search-traffic-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3EA%20new%20generation%20of%20media%20startups%20is%20built%20to%20survive%20'Google%20Zero'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-search-reshapes-seo-fueling-geo-gold-rush-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3EThe%20new%20SEO%20is%20GEO%20%E2%80%94%20and%20no%20one%20really%20knows%20the%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-engine-alternatives-reddit-tiktok-ai-chatbots-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBored%20of%20Google%3F%20Here%20are%20the%20smartest%20ways%20to%20search%20the%20web.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStay%20tuned%20for%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhy%20Pinterest%20is%20all%20in%20on%20visual%20search%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20more%20existential%20questions.%20Chiefly%2C%20how%20can%20Google%20preserve%20a%20healthy%20web%20ecosystem%20once%20AI%20has%20eaten%20the%20internet%3F%20To%20keep%20pace%20with%20rivals%2C%20Google%20is%20reimagining%20search%20not%20as%20a%20directory%2C%20but%20a%20conversation%20that%20removes%20the%20hassle%20of%20scrolling%20and%20clicking.%20What%20that%20means%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20internet%20is%20a%20lingering%20question.%20Still%2C%20Google's%20business%20may%20not%20only%20survive%20its%20self-disruption%2C%20but%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20the%20users%2C%20and%20as%20long%20as%20it%20continues%20to%20rush%20out%20new%20products%2C%20no%20one%20can%20match%20its%20distribution%20tentacles%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20Google%20executive%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20come%20out%20as%20winners%20no%20matter%20the%20scenario.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20through%20platform%20shifts%20before%2C%20and%20every%20time%20it's%20been%20an%20expansionary%20moment%20for%20Google%20and%20for%20Search.%20We%20move%20quickly%2C%20innovate%2C%20and%20create%20new%20opportunities%20for%20our%20products%2C%20partners%2C%20and%20users%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20what%20we're%20doing%20with%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22369cea76-fb23-484f-b79e-08de8580b7bb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGemini%20rising%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDid%20Google%20see%20it%20coming%3F%20That%20depends%20on%20who%20you%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20rolled%20out%2C%20Googlers%20experienced%20a%20mix%20of%20frustration%20and%20relief.%20Some%20employees%20had%20worked%20on%20similar%20projects%20that%20had%20never%20made%20it%20outside%20Google's%20walls%2C%20and%20seeing%20a%20much%20smaller%20competitor%20take%20the%20glory%20was%20frustrating.%20Others%20saw%20it%20as%20the%20starting%20pistol%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20and%20the%20green%20light%20for%20Google%20to%20finally%20unleash%20its%20own%20AI%20on%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20never%20lacked%20brains%20or%20technology.%20Employees%20at%20DeepMind%2C%20an%20AI%20research%20lab%20within%20Google's%20parent%20company%2C%20had%20been%20toying%20with%20large%20language%20models%20by%20the%20time%20ChatGPT%20appeared%2C%20but%20leaders%20worried%20that%20releasing%20a%20chatbot%20prone%20to%20bias%20or%20errors%20would%20spark%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20not%20intended%20as%20a%20public%20thing%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20DeepMind%20employee%20who%20worked%20on%20Google's%20own%20LLM%20technology%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20shortcomings%20and%20saw%20it%20start%20to%20be%20interesting%2C%20but%20it%20was%20unclear%20how%20to%20get%20it%20to%20be%20completely%20useful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20surprised%20some%20leaders%20inside%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20and%20where%20Google%20ultimately%20miscalculated%2C%20insiders%20say%20%E2%80%94%20was%20that%20users%20largely%20didn't%20seem%20to%20care%20about%20ChatGPT's%20shortcomings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Demis%20Hassabis%20and%20Sundar%20Pichai%20on%20stage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ad7797194a2d49b8af2967%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%202023%2C%20Google%20fused%20together%20two%20of%20its%20AI%20labs%20to%20focus%20on%20building%20Gemini.%3Cp%3EGLENN%20CHAPMAN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20DeepMind%2C%20teams%20scrambled%20to%20launch%20their%20answer%20to%20ChatGPT%2C%20a%20chatbot%20named%20Sparrow%2C%20which%20would%20have%20had%20more%20safety%20guardrails%20than%20ChatGPT%2C%20according%20to%20people%20who%20worked%20on%20it.%20That%20project%20soon%20died%20once%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-deepmind-org-chart-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20merged%20DeepMind%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20its%20internal%20AI%20lab%20Brain%2C%20and%20the%20company%20then%20put%20all%20its%20focus%20on%20Gemini.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Google%20made%20an%20internal%20push%20to%20infuse%20generative%20AI%20into%20all%20its%20most%20crucial%20products%2C%20including%20Search%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Android.%20It%20launched%20multiple%20iterations%20of%20the%20Gemini%20chatbot%2C%20the%20latest%20of%20which%20is%20Gemini%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef545791-542f-4b51-81be-52610cac5bc8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESearching%20for%20Google's%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20Google%20has%20made%20disrupting%20itself%20look%20fairly%20easy.%20The%20company%20just%20reported%20its%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-is-closing-the-gap-on-chatgpt-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24100%20billion%20quarter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20cloud%20business%2C%20which%20has%20long%20been%20second-fiddle%20to%20Amazon's%20and%20Microsoft's%2C%20is%20whirring%20into%20overdrive.%20Its%20specialized%20AI%20chips%2C%20for%20years%20an%20internal%20and%20slow-moving%20effort%2C%20are%20suddenly%20seeing%20blockbuster%20demand%20from%20companies%20vying%20for%20more%20computing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrent%20and%20former%20employees%20say%20Google's%20greatest%20advantage%20is%20that%20it%20owns%20the%20full%20technology%20stack%20needed%20to%20meet%20the%20AI%20boom.%20It%20offers%20numerous%20products%2C%20including%20Gemini%2C%20Search%2C%20and%20Maps%2C%20which%20are%20already%20used%20by%20billions%20of%20people.%20It%20has%20a%20fleet%20of%20researchers%20building%20frontier%20AI%20models.%20And%20it%20has%20a%20cloud%20infrastructure%20that%20is%20not%20just%20powering%20all%20these%20internal%20efforts%2C%20but%20that%20its%20biggest%20competitors%20are%20paying%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESearch%2C%20however%2C%20remains%20Google's%20core%20business%20and%20the%20boat%20it%20spent%20decades%20trying%20not%20to%20rock.%20When%20cofounders%20Larry%20Page%20and%20Sergey%20Brin%20started%20Google%2C%20it%20had%20no%20clear%20business%20model%20beyond%20building%20a%20world-beating%20search%20engine%2C%20but%20the%20founders%20were%20eventually%20swayed%20into%20putting%20ads%20into%20search%20results.%20It%20became%20one%20of%20the%20most%20scalable%20businesses%20ever%20imagined%20in%20the%20digital%20era%2C%20and%20to%20this%20day%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20provide%20the%20largest%20chunk%20of%20Google's%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google%20Search%20lead%20Liz%20Reid%20speaking%20on%20stage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6630f9e8ec0c696569ff0b0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20Search%20head%20Liz%20Reid%3Cp%3ESAJJAD%20HUSSAIN%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Google%20must%20figure%20out%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-overviews-search-engine-new-openai-searchgpt-competition-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20Overviews%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20its%20generated%20summaries%20that%20give%20users%20instant%20answers%20to%20their%20questions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20more%20dramatic%20reimagining%20of%20search%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-mode-search-gemini-results-chatgpt-overviews-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20Mode%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20as%20much%20juice%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20search%20advertising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20can't%20afford%20to%20stand%20still.%20Industry%20analysts%20at%20EMARKETER%2C%20Business%20Insider's%20sister%20company%2C%20predict%20Google's%20share%20of%20the%20search%20ads%20market%20will%20drop%20below%2050%25%20for%20the%20first%20time%20next%20year%20(a%20revision%20to%20their%20earlier%20prediction%20that%20it%20would%20happen%20in%202025).%20By%20the%20end%20of%202026%2C%20EMARKETER%20predicts%20Google%20will%20have%20a%2048.9%25%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEMARKETER%20senior%20forecast%20analyst%20Oscar%20Orozco%20said%20that%20the%20sustained%20high%20performance%20of%20Google's%20search%20business%20suggests%20advertiser%20caution%20around%20AI%20Overviews%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Boverblown%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20this%20does%20remain%20a%20long-term%20threat%20for%20their%20search%20business%2C%20and%20we%20believe%20as%20LLMs%20monetize%20their%20search%20capabilities%2C%20Google%20will%20continue%20to%20lose%20share%2C%20albeit%20at%20a%20slower%20rate%20than%20we%20had%20expected%20at%20this%20same%20time%20last%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a66255a8-32f4-4f03-9bb3-4ef8346dac3e%5C%22%3EGoogle%20is%20reshaping%20the%20web%20as%20we%20know%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%2C%20at%20least%20publicly%2C%20doesn't%20appear%20to%20be%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpodcasts%2Fwsj-the-future-of-everything%2Fthe-google-exec-reinventing-search-in-the-ai-era%2F52d5bc85-7056-40a7-b790-04079a2c44d7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Google%20Search%20boss%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogles-vision-for-search-in-an-ai-era-gemini-io-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELiz%20Reid%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20while%20changes%20to%20search%20resulted%20in%20reduced%20traffic%20to%20some%20websites%2C%20the%20overall%20number%20of%20search%20queries%20was%20increasing%20because%20Google%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20people%20to%20get%20to%20answers%2C%20either%20through%20AI%20Overviews%20or%20tools%20like%20Lens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20increase%20in%20searches%20sort%20of%20compensates%20for%20the%20impact%20on%20ads%20clicks%20such%20that%20we%20end%20up%20roughly%20at%20the%20same%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Reid%20said.%20She%20also%20made%20a%20point%20that%20chatbots%20can't%20replace%20products%20users%20are%20looking%20to%20buy%2C%20hinting%20at%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20Google%3A%20transactional%20searches%20that%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20produce%20ad%20revenue%20for%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20that%20is%20changing%20for%20Google.%20The%20search%20funnel%20%E2%80%94%20the%20time%20between%20someone%20beginning%20to%20research%20a%20product%20to%20hitting%20%26quot%3Bbuy%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20is%20shrinking%2C%20as%20generative%20AI%20gets%20people%20to%20what%20they%20want%20sooner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-shopping-ads-agents-marketing-advertisers-tools-search-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20has%20begun%20to%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20world%20how%20it's%20adapting%20to%20protect%20its%20core%20moneymaker.%20However%2C%20it's%20unclear%20what%20the%20generative%20AI%20boom%20means%20for%20the%20long-term%20health%20of%20the%20web%2C%20and%20how%20it%20will%20impact%20websites%20that%20supply%20information%20as%20opposed%20to%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20says%20that%20its%20new%20AI%20search%20features%20can%20help%20users%20find%20more%20relevant%20content%2C%20and%20that%20queries%20continue%20to%20grow%20year-over-year.%20Yet%20many%20publishers%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emarketer.com%2Fcontent%2Fgoogle-ai-overviews-decrease-referral-traffic-much-25%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esee%20search%20traffic%20declining%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedia-startups-post-google-zero-search-traffic-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrowing%20anxieties%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20even%20if%20overall%20searches%20go%20up%20with%20AI%20summaries%2C%20they%20will%20not%20translate%20into%20website%20clicks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20Pew%20Research%20study%20based%20on%20the%20search%20history%20of%20900%20users%20concluded%20that%20when%20an%20AI%20Overview%20appeared%2C%20users%20clicked%20a%20traditional%20link%208%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20compared%20to%2015%25%20when%20an%20AI%20summary%20didn't%20appear.%20Google%20said%20the%20research%20was%20flawed%20and%20not%20representative%20of%20overall%20search%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELily%20Ray%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20SEO%20research%20firm%20Amsive%2C%20said%20that%20a%20shift%20to%20an%20AI-first%20Google%20would%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20publishers%20and%20content%20creators%20who%20build%20much%20of%20the%20web%20to%20make%20money.%20If%20people%20stop%20publishing%2C%20where%20will%20Google%20get%20the%20information%20it%20needs%20to%20construct%20its%20AI%20Overviews%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20how%20they%20plan%20to%20solve%20that%3B%20their%20current%20excuses%20are%20not%20cutting%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20idea%20she%20suggested%20is%20that%20Google%20and%20other%20AI%20companies%20that%20build%20large%20language%20models%20pay%20commissions%20to%20the%20sites%20they%20train%20on%20or%20reference%2C%20as%20an%20incentive%20for%20them%20to%20keep%20creating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20not%20alone%20in%20feeling%20something%20needs%20to%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20business%20model%20of%20the%20web%20can't%20survive%20unless%20there's%20some%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Cloudflare%20CEO%20Matthew%20Prince%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Prince%2C%20whose%20business%20acts%20as%20a%20gateway%20between%20websites%20and%20the%20internet%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatthew-prince-search-engines-ai-cloudflare-google-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%