2%2C%20and%20I%20like%20to%20start%20every%20day%20thinking%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20great%20one.%20If%20I%20have%20a%20meeting%2C%20it's%20set%20even%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20problem%20is%2C%20I%20hit%20the%20snooze%20button%20once%20or%20twice.%20It%20is%20not%20good%20if%20I%20hit%20it%20three%20times%2C%20which%20means%20I%20won't%20be%20up%20until%20around%206%3A30.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e2e0cdaa-9cd6-4b22-b1cc-2a575b4d0d51%5C%22%3EI'm%20online%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20get%20out%20of%20bed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20enemy%20might%20be%20that%20I%20have%20two%20phones.%20I%20have%20a%20personal%20device%20and%20a%20work%20device.%20By%20the%20time%20I've%20gotten%20up%20out%20of%20bed%2C%20I%20have%20already%20looked%20at%20both%20to%20see%20if%20anything%20was%20urgent%20from%20the%20night%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20become%20the%20enemy%20when%20I%20become%20distracted%20and%20lose%20focus.%20I%20try%20to%20be%20disciplined%20about%20setting%20both%20aside%20at%20times%20and%20frankly%20shutting%20down%20all%20screens%2C%20but%20I%20am%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe4a5bdc-3cce-4e61-8e44-66d2541f75fd%5C%22%3EI%20plan%20my%20outfits%20in%20advance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22787%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donna%20Morris%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691f81c289026fbb4d0e19f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22590%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMorris%20said%20she%20likes%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20she's%20wearing%20in%20advance.%3Cp%3EWalmart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20pretty%20organized.%20The%20night%20before%20work%2C%20sometimes%20even%20as%20early%20as%20Sunday%20night%2C%20I'll%20figure%20out%20what%20I'm%20going%20to%20wear%20during%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20there%20are%20certain%20individuals%20who%20probably%20wear%20the%20exact%20same%20thing%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20one%20of%20those%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20going%20out%20to%20a%20store%20or%20a%20club%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20wear%20denim%20of%20some%20sort%2C%20probably%20a%20T-shirt%20and%20a%20jacket%2C%20and%20always%20my%20Walmart%20badge%20and%20running%20shoes%20or%20really%20comfortable%20sneakers.%20That's%20different%20from%20how%20I%20dress%20when%20I%20come%20into%20our%20office%2C%20where%20I'll%20probably%20be%20a%20bit%20more%20formal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3acaea3-baa7-4ab2-86dd-7c8a9a4f67c1%5C%22%3EI%20listen%20to%20CNN's%20podcast%20and%20the%20'Today'%20show%20while%20getting%20ready%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMale%20leaders%20can%20probably%20get%20ready%20in%2015%20minutes.%20They%20can%20probably%20get%20up%2C%20wash%20their%20hair%2C%20and%20away%20they%20go.%20Female%20leaders%20take%20longer%20to%20get%20ready.%20So%2C%20rightly%20or%20wrongly%2C%20it%20takes%20me%20longer%20to%20get%20ready%2C%20and%20it%20depends%20on%20whether%20it's%20a%20wash-your-hair%20day%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20my%20own%20hair%20every%20other%20day.%20I've%20never%20been%20the%20type%20to%20not%20do%20that.%20I%20budget%20about%2045%20minutes%20to%20an%20hour%20to%20get%20ready%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20get%20ready%2C%20I%20listen%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BCNN%205%20Things%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20and%20I%20always%20have%20the%20%26quot%3BToday%26quot%3B%20show%20on%2C%20because%20I%20also%20want%20to%20hear%20about%20what's%20happening%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ac044ee-ce9c-48c0-901f-26aaeaf75ee8%5C%22%3EIt%20takes%20me%20five%20minutes%20to%20get%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20it%20even%20takes%20me%20five%20minutes%20to%20get%20to%20the%20office.%20That%20was%20very%20deliberate.%20I%20try%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20office%20between%208%3A15%20and%208%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20and%20then%20I%20start%20my%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a9331d6-8613-474b-865e-2fba2762db4b%5C%22%3EI%20have%20back-to-back%20meetings%20starting%20at%208%3A35%20a.m.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221828%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donna%20Morris%20speaking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e271589026fbb4d0dfcd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221230%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMorris%20figures%20out%20what%20she's%20going%20to%20wear%20ahead%20of%20time.%3Cp%3EWalmart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20day%20is%20typically%20spent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-chief-people-officer-shares-how-uses-ai-candidates-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emeeting%20great%20associates%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20work%20for%20us%20or%20might%20be%20interested%20in%20working%20for%20us%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20typical%20day%2C%20I%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-walmart-is-emerging-as-an-ai-powerhouse-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eback-to-back%20schedule%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20meetings%20tend%20to%20start%20at%20five%20minutes%20past%20the%20half%20hour.%20My%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20day%20is%20at%208%3A35%20a.m.%2C%20unless%20I'm%20meeting%20with%20some%20of%20my%20peers%20who%20start%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f21cb2e1-bd65-47d9-8315-1e6ebcc11084%5C%22%3EI've%20never%20tried%20coffee%20or%20tea%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20drink%20Diet%20Coke%20every%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20five%20years%20old%2C%20I%20burned%20my%20mouth%20so%20badly%20that%20I%20was%20afraid%20to%20drink%20anything%20hot%20for%20years.%20I've%20just%20never%20been%20a%20hot%20drink%20type%20of%20girl%2C%20I%20guess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20limit%20myself%20to%20two%20Diet%20Cokes%20a%20day%2C%20although%20every%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20I%20sneak%20in%20a%20third.%20I%20typically%20don't%20drink%20it%20before%2010%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d78edbb-aec8-411a-9a24-c6744b417ac4%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20have%20big%20meals%20during%20the%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20big%20meals%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20at%20lunch%2C%20but%20I%20am%20a%20believer%20in%20having%20something%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20on%20a%20routine%20of%20doing%20overnight%20oats%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20then%20I'd%20have%20two%20hard-boiled%20eggs%20every%20lunch.%20But%20I%20recently%20received%20feedback%20that%20I%20should%20do%20my%20protein%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20overnight%20oats%20at%20noon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0a10a2c-921f-4ddb-9c4a-125ff0c3eb15%5C%22%3EI%20stay%20at%20the%20office%20until%206%3A30%20p.m.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221833%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donna%20Morris%20standing%20on%20a%20stage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691f7e35abd5e944effb2e58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMorris%20said%20she%20stays%20at%20work%20until%20about%206%3A30%20p.m.%3Cp%3EWalmart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tend%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20office%20and%20work%20until%20around%206%20or%206%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20when%20there%20are%20fewer%20people%20around%20and%20I%20can%20have%20some%20quiet%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20go%20home%2C%20and%20if%20I'm%20really%20fortunate%2C%20my%20husband%20is%20home.%20He's%20a%20fantastic%20cook%2C%20so%20I%20benefit%20when%20he's%20in%20Bentonville%20with%20me.%20When%20he's%20not%20with%20me%2C%20it%20means%20I%20need%20to%20be%20more%20organized%2C%20because%20I%20have%20to%20cook%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20fantastic%20cookbooks%20because%20buying%20cookbooks%20is%20something%20I'm%20passionate%20about.%20However%2C%20I'm%20not%20as%20good%20at%20cooking%2C%20so%20I%20end%20up%20on%20the%20same%20rinse-and-repeat%20meal%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d4a9f39-497b-44e8-9925-690c8a215b6c%5C%22%3EM