ngsters%20who%20operated%20at%20the%20Mississippi%20border.%20The%20sheriff%20would%20later%20tell%20law%20enforcement%20that%20an%20anonymous%20person%20called%20his%20Adamsville%20home%20just%20before%205%20a.m.%20and%20insisted%20he%20drive%20to%20the%20state%20line%2C%20about%2025%20minutes%20away.%20Buford%20said%20Pauline%20was%20suspicious%20about%20the%20call%20%E2%80%94%20with%20reason.%20Since%20cleaning%20up%20McNairy%20County%2C%20the%20sheriff%20had%20survived%20multiple%20gunshot%20and%20stab%20wounds.%20He%20said%20she%20thought%20it%20was%20best%20to%20go%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Buford%20and%20Pauline%20Pusser%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6920887789026fbb4d0e270e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBuford%20Pusser%20and%20Pauline%20Pusser.%3Cp%3EMcNairy%20County%20Archives%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20dawn%2C%20they%20got%20in%20Buford's%20squad%20car%20and%20started%20down%20the%20quiet%20two-way%20street%20to%20State%20Line%20Road.%20Buford%20would%20later%20tell%20investigators%20that%20about%2020%20miles%20later%2C%20on%20New%20Hope%20Road%2C%20a%20car%20with%20no%20headlights%20sped%20up%20beside%20the%20Pussers%20and%20began%20shooting.%20Pauline%20was%20hit.%20He%20floored%20the%20accelerator%2C%20pulled%20off%20to%20one%20side%2C%20and%20frantically%20searched%20for%20where%20his%20wife%20had%20been%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20speeding%20driver%20reappeared%2C%20pulled%20up%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20road%2C%20and%20fired%20again%2C%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20fatally%20shooting%20Pauline%20in%20the%20forehead.%20Buford%2C%20who%20ended%20up%20with%20a%20bullet%20wound%20on%20his%20left%20jaw%2C%20said%20the%20assailants%20peeled%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeadlines%20chronicled%20the%20shocking%20incident%3A%20One%20blared%2C%20%26quot%3BMCNAIRY%20S