s%20in%20a%20downturn%2C%20but%20specialty%20chemicals%20might%20offer%20a%20bright%20spot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshaun-maguire-sequoia-vc-gop-trump-supporter-backlash-zohran-mamdani-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShaun%20Maguire%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Sequoia%20Capital%20and%20early%20investor%20in%20several%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20companies%2C%20says%20people%20aren't%20focusing%20on%20niche%20chemicals%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BRelentless%26quot%3B%20podcast%20that%20aired%20on%20November%2017%2C%20Maguire%20said%20that%20he%20might%20invest%20in%20the%20chemicals%20industry%20if%20he%20had%20%2410%20billion%20to%20start%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20chemicals%20industry%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20underrated%20industries%20in%20the%20world%20for%20many%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20Maguire%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20most%20people%20don't%20think%20about%20the%20industry%2C%20which%20supports%20production%20for%20nearly%20all%20commercial%20and%20household%20goods%2C%20according%20to%20a%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cisa.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-02%2Fchemical_sector_profile_final_508_2022_0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Cybersecurity%20and%20Infrastructure%20Security%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20those%20who%20do%20know%20about%20the%20industry%20don't%20fully%20understand%20it%2C%20thinking%20of%20it%20as%20strictly%20a%20commodity%20industry%2C%20Maguire%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20a%20large%20fraction%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20I'd%20say%20at%20least%2025%25%2C%20is%20hardcore%20specialty%20chemicals%20that%20are%20actually%20very%20rare.%20A%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20there's%20only%20one%20company%20in%20the%20world%20that%20will%20make%20some%20specialty%20chemical%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20(Specialty%20chemicals%20accounted%20for%20about%2023%25%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20according%20to%20CISA's%20report).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaguire%20said%20that%20those%20chemicals%20can%20be%20crucial%20for%20another%20company's%20production%2C%20as%20he%20said%20is%20true%20of%20one%20of%20Musk's%20businesses%2C%20and%20that%20losing%20access%20to%20a%20key%20chemical%20can%20severely%20delay%20or%20upend%20projects.%20Specialty%20chemicals%20include%20%26quot%3Badhesives%2C%20sealants%2C%20flavors%20and%20fragrances%2C%20food%20additives%2C%20and%20explosives%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cisa.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2025-08%2FChemical_Sector_Risk_Management_Agency_Fact_Sheet_508.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECISA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chemical%20industry%20is%20in%20a%20downcycle%2C%20and%20production%20volumes%20are%20expected%20to%20contract%20by%200.2%25%20next%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Deloitte's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deloitte.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Finsights%2Findustry%2Fchemicals-and-specialty-materials%2Fchemical-industry-outlook.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2026%20Chemical%20Industry%20Outlook.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Though%20the%20report%20predicts%20continued%20overcapacity%20in%20basic%20chemicals%2C%20it%20found%20that%20specialty%20chemicals%20are%20earning%20higher%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpecialty%20chemicals%20tend%20to%20be%20less%20commoditized%20and%20avoid%20the%20hyper-competitiveness%20of%20the%20commodity%20chemicals%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20chemical%20demand%20in%20the%20construction%2C%20automotive%2C%20and%20consumer%20goods%20industries%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%20suffering%2C%20the%20semiconductor%20market%20may%20offer%20a%20bright%20spot%2C%20according%20to%20Deloitte's%20report.%20The%20boom%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5